WEBVTT

00:00:07.695 --> 00:00:11.532 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All of you will be stumbled
in connection with me on this night.

00:00:13.701 --> 00:00:17.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Peter thought he was strong
and would never make Jehovah sad.

00:00:19.164 --> 00:00:22.418 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But doing the right thing

00:00:22.418 --> 00:00:24.545 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
isn’t always easy.

00:00:27.673 --> 00:00:30.009 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ll never make Jehovah sad!

00:00:31.635 --> 00:00:34.179 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We know you’d never want to.

00:00:36.891 --> 00:00:41.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What if Jehovah doesn’t want
to be my Friend anymore?

00:00:41.729 --> 00:00:43.898 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Peter knew the right thing to do.

00:00:43.898 --> 00:00:45.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But he was afraid

00:00:45.941 --> 00:00:48.027 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and did the wrong thing.

00:00:48.777 --> 00:00:50.988 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But he didn’t give up.

00:00:50.988 --> 00:00:52.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Do you know why?

